                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_020-9a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T14:23:35.071+09:00">no matter whether he was blind or not. German "ob er nun blind war oder nicht, in jedem dieser beiden Faelle".</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_016-39a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-27T17:46:40.713+09:00">孔子的死亡</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_028-2a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-27T18:26:49.54+09:00">"a teacher of the caliber of Confucius"</seg>
