                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_028-2a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-27T18:35:44.357+09:00">then people like those 70 disciples (of Confucius)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_028-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-27T18:36:18.39+09:00">will be our present Confucians.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_047-17a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-27T19:02:59.617+09:00">predictive knowledge about clouds and rain</seg>
